Use the standard library
This is how to specialFilter of nums:
  Remember that count is 0
  Do this nums's length times:
    Remember that n is item count in nums
    When n is more than 0, then:
      Remember that lastDigit is remainder of n and 10
      Remember that firstDigit is quotient of n and 10
      Do this 20 times:
        When firstDigit is at most 9, then:
          Leave the loop
        End when
        Remember that firstDigit is quotient of firstDigit and 10
      End do
      When firstDigit is 5, then:
        When lastDigit is 5, then:
          Increase count by 1
        End when
      End when
    End when
    Increase count by 1
  End do
  The answer is diff of count and nums's length
